title: Kubernetes: Daemon Pods
agents: kubernetes
catalog: containerization/kubernetes
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check and the associated special agent (agent_kubernetes) are deprecated
 and will be removed in Checkmk version 2.2.0.

 Please configure the new special agent using the "Kubernetes" ruleset.

 This check monitors the status of the daemon pods in a
 kubernetes cluster.

 The check returns {OK} if the desired number of nodes has been
 scheduled and every node is available, otherwise it returns {WARN}.

discovery:
 One service is created.
